title: Fixer Upper S03E01 Searching for Small Town Charm HDTV.x264-JIVE
description:
Fixer+Upper - Season 3, Episode 1




Finding Small Town Texas Charm for a Young Family

Chip and Joanna take their new clients, Noah and Jessica Dansby, on a tour through three homes in Hillsboro, Texas, a small charming city halfway between Dallas and Waco. The Dansby family currently lives in Hillsboro and want to stay. Chip and Jo find three houses that could potentially provide the Dansbys with the space and character they're looking for. Can Chip and Jo find the perfect home for this growing family? What will the first design meeting be like at the Silos? Will Chip remember his twelfth anniversary?




Original Air Date: 01-Dec-2015
